---
title: Chicken Rigatoni with Crème Fraîche and Tarragon
description: Our recipes are rigorously tested here at the Fresh Farm but André knows he's onto a particular winner when his kids give something the double thumbs up. There are plenty of appreciative noises around the table when he dishes this one up and we can see why. Comforting pasta, tender chicken and a delicious creamy sauce with just the right amount of tarragon. We're sure you'll give it the thumbs up too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-rigatoni-wk44-74b27a21-bc0b02eb.jpg
